{"tid":683451,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"毛記葵涌全年盈利跌近81%","createTime":"2018-05-29T16:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:17:44.000Z","uid":166462,"like":349,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"569a67f28f898fb1a2769c178036b39f9cff45e2","tid":683451,"uid":166462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"毛記葵涌全年盈利跌近81% 印刷媒體虧損擴大逾兩倍<br />\n香港電台-財經\t香港電台-財經2018年5月29日4 則留言<br />\n毛記葵涌公布，截至3月底止，全年盈利約692萬港元，按年跌近81%，不派末期息。<br />\n<br />\n撇除約1620萬元的上市開支，經調整盈利2310萬元，按年仍跌36.4%。<br />\n<br />\n全年收入近8675萬元，按年跌8.9%。期內，毛利率51.3%，按年下降9.9個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n按業務劃分，數碼媒體服務盈利跌10.7%至3229萬元，印刷媒體服務虧損擴大2.3倍至332萬元。<br />\n<br />\nFROM YAHOO<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565d08b82bc427985618b842150f97897f918389","tid":683451,"uid":64345,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:17:26.000Z","msg":"cap完水，理你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae149c56ffbb022cb6dc306383441a8621f73f2","tid":683451,"uid":62646,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾始終都係垃圾"},{"pid":"ad66b8445c03fca3427a158b6aa600c6d86d40ed","tid":683451,"uid":57797,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:00:04.000Z","msg":"元秋好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ce08c8715af17b6590824e62b7ddb1075b4033","tid":683451,"uid":10757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有盈利"},{"pid":"c31e9132190ecdeb8548a89db82e5e5ad02565a2","tid":683451,"uid":52595,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score